data.description: Unleash your potential in this sprawling 4-bedroom haven! Enjoy the sunshine streaming through the open floor plan, whip up culinary delights in the well-equipped kitchen, and cozy up by the fireplace in the inviting living room. This expansive home offers space for everything you need, plus a bonus 1-bedroom garage apartment for endless possibilities. Imagine grilling under the stars in your private backyard oasis, knowing you have the freedom to personalize your space without HOA restrictions. This updated home offers peace of mind with recent plumbing work and HVAC upgrades, all ready for you to create lasting memories. Don't miss your chance to own a piece of paradise - schedule your viewing today!
